Items.Name: iPhone 6/6s Plus Reusable On The Go Shadow Edition Privacy Screen Protector
Items.ShortDescription: Have you ever wanted a privacy screen but only for a short period of time?

03e3cfb3-934b-4bad-ad35-40dbe4300da7.Name: iPhone 6/6s Plus Reusable On The Go Shadow Edition Privacy Screen Protector
03e3cfb3-934b-4bad-ad35-40dbe4300da7.ShortDescription: Have you ever wanted a privacy screen but only for a short period of time?
03e3cfb3-934b-4bad-ad35-40dbe4300da7.LongDescription:
Have you ever wanted a privacy screen but only for a short period of time? Yes! Everyone's answer is YES! Gadget Guard has found and created the solution! This item is reusable and easily stored when not in use. This item is used as an add to to other forms of screen protection, used in addition to the other products such as the Original, Shadow Edition, or Black Ice. When you are not concerned about wandering eyes this privacy protector is easily stored in the plastic plate storage that is included in your purchase.

Features

  • Secondary back up privacy screen
  • Two Way(Side View) Privacy
  • Reusable, store when not in use
  • Long Lasting Adhesive, easily cleaned

M632536.Name: iPhone 7 Plus Performance Ultra Case
M632536.LongDescription:
Offering premium protection for your new iPhone, the Performance Series Ultra Protection Case is composed of quad-layer defense technology. The dual infused scratch-resistant outer shell is tough against harmful drops and dents, while the interior impact ridge delivers military grade shock absorption. The Ultra Protection Case delivers outstanding drop protection while maintaining a sleek profile.

Features

  • Two-piece design
  • Impact ridge provides military grade drop protection
  • Integrated buttons
  • Shock absorbing honeycomb texture
